OL,3,CCleveland Police could be abolished as
OL,4,Cgovernment plans major policing shake-
OL,5,Cup
OL,7,FMajor changes to the makeup of England
OL,8,Fand Wales' police forces are expected
OL,9,Fto be announced this week, including
OL,10,Fthe possible abolition of Cleveland
OL,11,FPolice, the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,12,FService reports.
OL,14,FThe government is publishing a white
OL,15,Fpaper outlining its plans on Wednesday
OL,16,F28 January, which could see a large
OL,17,Freduction in the number of police
OL,18,Fforces.
