OL,3,CCleveland Police could be abolished as
OL,4,Cgovernment plans major policing shake-
OL,5,Cup
OL,7,FThe North East currently has three
OL,8,Fpolice forces: Cleveland Police, which
OL,9,Fcovers Middlesbrough, Stockton, Redcar
OL,10,Fand Hartlepool, Durham Constabulary,
OL,11,Fwhich includes County Durham and
OL,12,FDarlington, and Northumbria Police,
OL,13,Fwhich oversees Northumberland and Tyne
OL,14,Fand Wear.
OL,16,FHome Secretary pledges faster 999
OL,17,Fresponse and more officers on the
OL,18,Fstreets in major police reforms
