OL,3,CCleveland Police could be abolished as
OL,4,Cgovernment plans major policing shake-
OL,5,Cup
OL,7,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood is
OL,8,Fexpected to announce that new, larger
OL,9,Fforces will focus on tackling serious
OL,10,Fand organised crime, as well as
OL,11,Fcomplex cases.
OL,13,FMahmood is also thought to be
OL,14,Fannouncing new Local Policing Areas
OL,15,Ffor every town, borough, or city.
OL,16,FLocal officers in these areas would
OL,17,Ffocus on neighbourhood policing and
OL,18,Flocal crime.
