OL,3,CCleveland Police could be abolished as
OL,4,Cgovernment plans major policing shake-
OL,5,Cup
OL,7,FThe government has previously
OL,8,Fconfirmed it will abolish Police and
OL,9,FCrime Commissioners (PCCs) from May
OL,10,F2028, when regional mayors will absorb
OL,11,Ftheir powers.
OL,13,FIt is not clear what the make-up of
OL,14,Fthe new police forces would be.
OL,16,FIn an interview with BBC Radio Tees
OL,17,Fearlier this month, Tess Valley Mayor
OL,18,FBen Houchen discussed the possible
OL,19,Fchanges that could be introduced:
OL,21,FUse the River Tees
