OL,3,CCleveland Police could be abolished as
OL,4,Cgovernment plans major policing shake-
OL,5,Cup
OL,7,FIt could be that areas north of the
OL,8,FRiver Tees are absorbed into Durham
OL,9,FConstabulary, and areas south be
OL,10,Fabsorbed into North Yorkshire's force.
OL,12,FThis would mean the local authority of
OL,13,FStockton would be divided between two
OL,14,Fpolice forces.
OL,16,FThis change is said to be unlikely as
OL,17,Fit would not align with the mayoral
OL,18,Fareas.
