OL,3,CCleveland Police could be abolished as
OL,4,Cgovernment plans major policing shake-
OL,5,Cup
OL,7,FCleveland Police would still exist but
OL,8,Fwould also cover Darlington would no
OL,9,Flonger be part of Durham Constabulary.
OL,10,FInstead, all five boroughs which are
OL,11,Fpart of the Tees Valley Combined
OL,12,FAuthority would have the same police
OL,13,Fforce.
OL,15,FAlthough Cleveland would remain as a
OL,16,Frelatively small force, it would align
OL,17,Fwith the government's plans to give
OL,18,FPCC powers to mayors.
